=========================  Criminal Case 3269  =========================

    scshunt violated Rule 2143 by failing to publish the Promotor's
    report in the week Mon 27 Aug - Sun 02 Sep.

========================================================================

Caller:                                 FKA441344
Barred:                                 scshunt

Judge:                                  Murphy
Judgement:                              GUILTY/APOLOGY

